of problems in terms of functionality.

00:13:49.240 --> 00:13:54.039
He wants that as the main headline color,
and that just doesn't work.

00:13:54.040 --> 00:13:57.119
Number three, as a designer,

00:13:57.120 --> 00:14:01.719
