and nuance and all that stuff.

00:14:06.240 --> 00:14:11.640
If I'm being told to make the fonts
black and the background white,

00:14:12.200 --> 00:14:15.239
there goes my well-crafted
color hierarchy.

00:14:15.240 --> 00:14:17.879
Sometimes it can be a bummer,
and that's just a fear of mine.

00:14:17.880 --> 00:14:18.919
I want to create beauty,

00:14:18.920 --> 00:14:22.999
and I don't want to just
make everything black and white.

00:14:23.000 --> 00:14:25.893
Those are a few of the pain points.

00:14:26.320 --> 00:14:31.715
Everyone has those on their own
side and there's truth to both sides.

00:14:33.080 --> 00:14:34.559
