00:41:15.840 --> 00:41:17.679
We are not on different teams.

00:41:17.680 --> 00:41:20.325
We are a part of the same teams,

00:41:20.760 --> 00:41:24.199
but we've got different core
values and we've got to bring

00:41:24.200 --> 00:41:29.119
those values together
and be a team and see the bigger picture.

00:41:29.160 --> 00:41:32.879
I'm for sure guilty of this when we first
started working together,

00:41:32.880 --> 00:41:35.029
of being very silo-driven.

00:41:35.880 --> 00:41:39.240
Number one, present the data.

00:41:41.280 --> 00:41:42.493
It's out there and it tells

00:41:42.494 --> 00:41:45.079
a story of people
who are being overlooked.

00:41:45.080 --> 00:41:51.240
Number two, realize that accessible
