00:41:51.600 --> 00:41:53.199
Go to Apple, go to Microsoft.

00:41:53.200 --> 00:41:55.018
They're doing it well.

00:41:55.920 --> 00:41:57.920
It doesn't have to suck.

00:41:59.040 --> 00:42:00.599
That's what I care about as a designer.

00:42:00.600 --> 00:42:02.599
I don't want it to suck.

00:42:02.600 --> 00:42:06.639
Number three,
keep the content color fully accessible

00:42:06.640 --> 00:42:09.439
